<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_17ad0728-76ab-4c75-9dd5-4ba3948bd151" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>E2F1</sptc><title id="_d2af7f29-eb7f-45a0-b7ec-6c4cc987af5d">Adequate safeguards</title><archive-num> 2019: EF2.1</archive-num><subclause id="_3f0db619-5b8a-4d1b-9ef1-d96742caca5a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_887619c9-92fe-4aec-8a98-04cb2e25fb95"/><num>1</num><p>A building is to be provided with safeguards so that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_2a9f76db-e7bb-43b7-9773-f9faae1ff5a0">occupants are warned of a fire in the building so that they may safely evacuate; and</li><li id="_5f0a0902-025a-497c-bfbf-49e4ec23456e">occupants have time to safely evacuate before the environment in any <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1261_2.0.0.xml#_dc98ef12-e47e-44ae-abca-010bd3db8c90" id="_93903bd5-06b5-427e-96ef-1de4fea86907" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">evacuation route</xref> becomes untenable from the effects of fire.</li></ol></subclause></clause>